13:45.575 --> 13:47.618
- Mike is in the quench.

13:47.618 --> 13:49.370
<i>- I start to see a warp</i>

13:49.370 --> 13:52.498
<i>and I know that I have</i>
<i>a short window of time,</i>

13:52.498 --> 13:55.877
<i>so I'm able to bend the blade</i>
<i>over my leg</i>

13:55.877 --> 13:57.420
<i>and get it back into shape.</i>

13:57.420 --> 14:02.633
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:02.633 --> 14:04.761
<i>- So other people are pretty</i>
<i>much finishing up</i>

14:04.761 --> 14:06.429
