14:06.429 --> 14:08.014
<i>and get it cut</i>
<i>to the right size</i>

14:08.014 --> 14:09.974
<i>'cause this thing is over</i>
<i>22 inches.</i>

14:09.974 --> 14:11.726
I don't even have to look
