14:11.726 --> 14:14.687
- Trystan's integral guard
has turned into

14:14.687 --> 14:16.564
some nasty looking needle
points.

14:16.564 --> 14:18.066
- Yeah, that's what I was
afraid of.

14:18.066 --> 14:19.567
- I guess if he had
to puncture something

14:19.567 --> 14:21.277
in a survival situation...
- [laughing]

14:21.277 --> 14:22.945
