14:32.580 --> 14:34.916
<i>♪ ♪</i>

14:34.916 --> 14:36.959
- And Trystan has quenched.

14:36.959 --> 14:38.544
<i>- So it turned out straight.</i>

14:38.544 --> 14:40.004
I just need to make sure
