14:41.881 --> 14:43.174
[bleep]

14:43.174 --> 14:45.259
And it just isn't hard.

14:45.259 --> 14:46.677
<i>My heart falls.</i>

14:46.677 --> 14:48.971
- So Trystan quenched
his blade.

14:48.971 --> 14:51.182
Now he's going back into
the forge.

14:51.182 --> 14:52.683
- If it was as simple
as giving my knife

14:52.683 --> 14:55.353
a Viagra, then mark my words,
