14:55.353 --> 14:57.855
- Every smith that comes
in here,

14:57.855 --> 15:01.442
that $10,000 is theirs for
the taking.

15:01.442 --> 15:04.028
And right here you have
a guy who is smiling

15:04.028 --> 15:07.156
and grinning, and yet hasn't
quenched his blade

15:07.156 --> 15:09.617
and there's only 40 seconds
left on the clock.

15:09.617 --> 15:12.495
This is a $10,000 gamble.

15:12.495 --> 15:14.163
- Why do you wait for
last minute?

15:14.163 --> 15:16.082
Now if plan A doesn't work,
you gotta do plan B,

15:16.082 --> 15:18.334
but do you have time
to do all that?

15:18.334 --> 15:22.004
- If I don't get this blade
