is only 10 and 5/8
inches long.

16:48.049 --> 16:51.177
That's 1 3/8 inches short
of the 12-inch minimum.

16:51.177 --> 16:54.472
<i>♪ ♪</i>

16:54.472 --> 16:57.767
- Brian, Mike, your blades met
all of our parameters.

16:57.767 --> 17:00.937
You'll be moving into the
second round of competition.

17:00.937 --> 17:05.316
Trystan, Doug, since today is
a Hollywood themed competition,

17:05.316 --> 17:08.027
