a little bit more dramatic.

17:08.027 --> 17:12.156
Your blades are entering
a sudden death match.

17:12.156 --> 17:14.116
- Honestly, my heart stopped.

17:14.116 --> 17:16.994
- Two blades enter,
one blade leaves.

17:16.994 --> 17:18.913
Your knives will be tested
on merit

17:18.913 --> 17:22.416
and you must earn a spot in
the next round or go home.

17:22.416 --> 17:24.794
We're gonna meet you
on the testing floor.

17:24.794 --> 17:26.879
<i>- This sudden death test</i>
<i>is most definitely</i>

17:26.879 --> 17:28.589
<i>gonna probably be brutal.</i>

17:28.589 --> 17:31.384
This is literally a make
or break moment for my knife.

17:31.384 --> 17:32.843
- Congratulations, gentlemen,

17:32.843 --> 17:35.012
you have the dubious
distinction of being

17:35.012 --> 17:38.224
our first two smiths to have
a sudden death elimination.

17:38.224 --> 17:40.476
I'm gonna be taking
your blades and batoning them

17:40.476 --> 17:42.228
into this industrial nut.

17:42.228 --> 17:43.854
Whoever's knife takes
the most damage

17:43.854 --> 17:45.856
will be asked to leave
The Forge.

17:45.856 --> 17:47.900
Trystan, you're up.

17:47.900 --> 17:49.402
<i>♪ ♪</i>

17:49.402 --> 17:51.404
<i>- I can't control myself</i>
<i>right now.</i>

17:51.404 --> 17:54.115
<i>My leg is just going, like,</i>
<i>50 miles an hour, shaking,</i>

17:54.115 --> 17:55.700
