18:24.895 --> 18:26.522
a little bit out of alignment.

18:26.522 --> 18:27.982
You can hear it.

18:27.982 --> 18:30.359
Other than that,
blade held up very well.

18:30.359 --> 18:31.819
- Thank you, sir.

18:31.819 --> 18:33.154
- Doug, you're up.

18:33.154 --> 18:35.072
<i>♪ ♪</i>

18:35.072 --> 18:37.241
<i>- Trystan's blade did really</i>
<i>nice in the test</i>

18:37.241 --> 18:39.076
<i>and it took a little bit of</i>
<i>damage.</i>

18:39.076 --> 18:40.578
That's gonna be a tough act
