and that it didn't

19:32.922 --> 19:34.632
<i>meet the parameters,</i>
<i>that's all on me.</i>

19:34.632 --> 19:36.509
I'll own that.

19:36.509 --> 19:39.011
I'll tell you what though,
I've made less than 100 knives,

19:39.011 --> 19:41.972
and I'm proud of what I did.

19:41.972 --> 19:45.017
<i>♪ ♪</i>

19:45.017 --> 19:46.769
- All right, Trystan,
