20:09.458 --> 20:11.043
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:11.043 --> 20:13.754
Trystan's come out of
that sudden death

20:13.754 --> 20:15.840
with renewed confidence
and strength

20:15.840 --> 20:17.758
in attempting this blade.

20:17.758 --> 20:20.469
- That's a brutal test,
