20:26.767 --> 20:29.311
<i>so I know that I have</i>
<i>a lot of work to do</i>

20:29.311 --> 20:31.522
<i>to catch up to these smiths.</i>

20:31.522 --> 20:34.692
<i>- We need to put a pommel</i>
