20:45.995 --> 20:48.497
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:48.497 --> 20:50.166
Did you bring enough
for everyone?

20:50.166 --> 20:51.709
- Oh.

20:51.709 --> 20:53.043
Oh yeah, I got it from
the concession stand.

20:53.043 --> 20:54.295
- [laughing]

20:54.295 --> 20:55.671
- Oh [bleep].

20:55.671 --> 20:57.506
<i>♪ ♪</i>

20:57.506 --> 21:00.134
- I really want to get
a better profile on the blade.

21:00.134 --> 21:02.094
I wanna have better edge
geometry.

21:02.094 --> 21:04.680
<i>I have a kind of an idea of</i>
<i>what I'ma do with the handle,</i>

21:04.680 --> 21:07.725
<i>but first I want to make sure</i>
<i>that it's a cutter.</i>

21:07.725 --> 21:09.310
- One hour has elapsed.

21:09.310 --> 21:12.354
You have two hours remaining
in this round.

21:12.354 --> 21:14.273
<i>- I get a 1/2 inch drill bit</i>
<i>in the drill press</i>

21:14.273 --> 21:16.734
<i>and I start drilling as far</i>
<i>down as I can go.</i>

21:16.734 --> 21:19.195
And that's gonna be one of
the easiest and fastest ways

21:19.195 --> 21:21.614
