21:28.454 --> 21:30.080
as you're hitting with it.

21:30.080 --> 21:31.916
<i>So to avoid my blade rolling</i>
<i>in the handle,</i>

21:31.916 --> 21:33.209
I'm gonna key it.

21:33.209 --> 21:35.669
- So it looks like Trystan's
basically

21:35.669 --> 21:37.129
