21:39.715 --> 21:42.092
It'll lock in.
- That's smart work.

21:42.092 --> 21:44.428
- Awesome.

21:44.428 --> 21:45.679
♪ ♪

21:45.679 --> 21:47.723
- Mike's got a very long
