22:09.328 --> 22:11.956
<i>The tang fits through</i>
<i>the handle really smoothly,</i>

22:11.956 --> 22:13.123
so now I'm really happy.

22:13.123 --> 22:16.794
<i>♪ ♪</i>

22:16.794 --> 22:20.005
- Brian is cutting a thick
piece of brass, man.

22:20.005 --> 22:21.423
<i>- I'm pretty confident</i>

22:21.423 --> 22:23.259
that my knife is where
